# Servidor
@urlServer = http://localhost:4000

### ============================================
### EVENTS - ENDPOINTS DE EVENTOS
### ============================================

### 1. GET - Listar todos os eventos
GET {{urlServer}}/events

### 2. GET - Buscar evento por ID
GET {{urlServer}}/events/8b7a5df3-6047-4769-b168-a3d89aa5cb37

### 3. POST - Criar novo evento
POST {{urlServer}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Curso Spring JPA",
  "type": 1,
  "dateTime": "2025-12-20T18:00:00",
  "startingSales": "2025-12-10T20:00:00",
  "endingSales": "2025-12-19T23:59:59",
  "price": 1500
}

### 4. PUT - Atualizar evento por ID
PUT {{urlServer}}/events/94facfad-2c94-43e3-aac3-5f1472cfe568
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Curso Spring JPA - Avançado",
  "type": 1,
  "dateTime": "2025-12-20T19:00:00",
  "startingSales": "2025-12-10T20:00:00",
  "endingSales": "2025-12-19T23:59:59",
  "price": 2000
}

### 5. DELETE - Deletar evento
DELETE {{urlServer}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "94facfad-2c94-43e3-aac3-5f1472cfe568"
}

### ============================================
### SALES - ENDPOINTS DE VENDAS
### ============================================

## 6. GET - Listar todas as vendas
GET {{urlServer}}/sales

### 7. GET - Buscar venda por ID
GET {{urlServer}}/sales/f037c710-dfb5-4a7e-8dc6-106d530db892

### 8. POST - Criar nova venda
POST {{urlServer}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "8b7a5df3-6047-4769-b168-a3d89aa5cb37",
  "userId": "8c66c443-509a-41a5-bf6d-9d795a978584"
}

### 9. PUT - Atualizar status da venda por ID
PUT {{urlServer}}/sales/c0b640a8-cfee-445e-bf2f-bcb5fffe9682
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PAGO"
}

### 10. DELETE - Deletar venda
DELETE {{urlServer}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "c0b640a8-cfee-445e-bf2f-bcb5fffe9682"
}
